      <bioghist id="aspace_def06b2fd068f3725d4b826d1f19176b">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Adrian Van Sinderen Prize was established in 1957 to encourage book collecting among undergraduates, book buying, and book-reading both as a hobby and as an integral part of the education process. A cash prize is awarded to a senior and to a sophomore.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_a7ace319bb4b7751606a3bf33399b532">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, completed applications, committee notes and memoranda, collection review schedules, and copies of press releases concerning the winners of the Adrian Van Sinderen Prize.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
